trans-unit.source: Represents the abstract class from which all implementations of the MD5 hash algorithm inherit.
trans-unit.target: Representerer den abstrakte klassen som arver fra alle implementeringer av MD5 hash-algoritmen.

trans-unit.source: Hash functions map binary strings of an arbitrary length to small binary strings of a fixed length.
trans-unit.target: Hash-funksjoner kartet binære strenger for en tilfeldig lengde til små binære strenger med en fast lengde.

trans-unit.source: A cryptographic hash function has the property that it is computationally infeasible to find two distinct inputs that hash to the same value; that is, hashes of two sets of data should match if the corresponding data also matches.
trans-unit.target: En kryptografisk hash-funksjonen har egenskapen at det er realistisk umulig å finne to ulike inndata som hash samme verdi; Det vil si samsvare numre for to sett med data hvis tilsvarende dataene oppfyller også.

trans-unit.source: Small changes to the data result in large, unpredictable changes in the hash.
trans-unit.target: Liten endringer i dataene føre til høyt, uforutsigbart endringer i hash-koden.

trans-unit.source: The hash size for the MD5 algorithm is 128 bits.
trans-unit.target: Hash-størrelse for MD5-algoritmen er 128 bits.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.HashAlgorithm.ComputeHash%2A> methods of the MD5 class return the hash as an array of 16 bytes.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.HashAlgorithm.ComputeHash%2A>metoder for klassen MD5 returnere hash-koden som en matrise av 16 byte.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.HashAlgorithm.ComputeHash%2A>

trans-unit.source: Note that some MD5 implementations produce a 32-character, hexadecimal-formatted hash.
trans-unit.target: Vær oppmerksom på at enkelte MD5 implementeringer gir en 32 tegn, heksadesimal-formatert hash-kode.

trans-unit.source: To interoperate with such implementations, format the return value of the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.HashAlgorithm.ComputeHash%2A> methods as a hexadecimal value.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil fungere sammen med slike implementeringer formatere returverdien for den <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.HashAlgorithm.ComputeHash%2A>metoder som en heksadesimal verdi.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.HashAlgorithm.ComputeHash%2A>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Newer hash functions, such as the Secure Hash Algorithms SHA-256 and SHA-512, are available.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Nyere hash-funksjoner, for eksempel sikre Hash-algoritmer SHA-256 og SHA-512 er tilgjengelige.

trans-unit.source: Consider using the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.SHA256> class or the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.SHA512> class instead of the MD5 class.
trans-unit.target: Vurder å bruke <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.SHA256>klasse eller <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.SHA512>klasse i stedet for MD5 klasse.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.SHA512> </xref:System.Security.Cryptography.SHA256>

trans-unit.source: Use MD5 only for compatibility with legacy applications and data.
trans-unit.target: Bruk MD5 bare for kompatibilitet med eldre programmer og data.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.MD5"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.MD5"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: To create an instance of the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.MD5> class, use the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.MD5.Create%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Opprette en forekomst av den <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.MD5>klasse, bruker du den <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.MD5.Create%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.MD5.Create%2A> </xref:System.Security.Cryptography.MD5>

trans-unit.source: Creates an instance of the default implementation of the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.MD5"></xref> hash algorithm.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en forekomst av standardimplementeringen av <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.MD5"> </xref> nummeralgoritme.

trans-unit.source: A new instance of the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.MD5"></xref> hash algorithm.
trans-unit.target: En ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.MD5"> </xref> nummeralgoritme.

trans-unit.source: The algorithm was used with Federal Information Processing Standards (FIPS) mode enabled, but is not FIPS compatible.
trans-unit.target: Algoritmen ble brukt med behandling av standarder FIPS (Federal Information)-modus aktivert, men er ikke FIPS-kompatibel.

trans-unit.source: Creates an instance of the specified implementation of the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.MD5"></xref> hash algorithm.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en forekomst av den angitte implementeringen av den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.MD5"> </xref> nummeralgoritme.

trans-unit.source: Possible values for `algName` are: `System.Security.Cryptography.MD5`, `MD5`, `System.Security.Cryptography.MD5CryptoServiceProvider`, and `System.Security.Cryptography.MD5Managed`.
trans-unit.target: Mulige verdier for `algName` er: `System.Security.Cryptography.MD5`, `MD5`, `System.Security.Cryptography.MD5CryptoServiceProvider`, og `System.Security.Cryptography.MD5Managed`.

trans-unit.source: The name of the specific implementation of <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.MD5"></xref> to use.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på bestemte implementeringen av <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.MD5"> </xref> skal brukes.

trans-unit.source: A new instance of the specified implementation of <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.MD5"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En ny forekomst av den angitte implementeringen av <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.MD5"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The algorithm described by the algName parameter was used with Federal Information Processing Standards (FIPS) mode enabled, but is not FIPS compatible.
trans-unit.target: Algoritmen beskrevet av det algName parameter ble brukt med behandling av standarder FIPS (Federal Information)-modus aktivert, men er ikke FIPS-kompatibel.
